profile:
Who we are , we are Ceci General Services Inc, we are a family owned business we have been in this business for over 15 years and continue to thrive with our reputation as James Hardie #1 preferred Installer in the Simcoe County Area!  We as a company thrive to bring out the best with it just being a small or big exterior renovation, a new build, a commercial build we are there for all your needs!

Our goal as a company is to listen to our clients, to deliver the best customer service as possible,
